original: Larsson, Carl-Gustav, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 24/12/10 i Sthlm av Carl L. o. Maria Karlsson. G. 33 m. Signe Johansson. Barn : Bo f. 42. — Stud :-ex. v. östra real i Sthlm 29, tandl:-kand. 31, tandläkare 33. Praktik i Linköping sed. 33.
translated: Larsson, Carl-Gustav, dentist, Linköping, b. 24/12/10 in Stockholm to Carl L. and Maria Karlsson. Married in 1933 to Signe Johansson. Children: Bo, born in 1942. Completed exams at Östra Real in Stockholm in 1929, dental studies in 1931, became a dentist in 1933. Practicing in Linköping since 1933.
